Kaaren Verne https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kaaren_Verne 0 Kaaren Verne (6 April 1918 – 23 December 1967), was a German-born actress. Sometimes billed as Karen Verne, she was originally a stage actress and member of the Berlin State Theatre. Kaaren_Verne ( 6_April_1918 – 23_December_1967 ) , was a_German-born_actress .
